Sources:

* This artwork was created using the following elements for a basis:
   - The Ubuntu logo provided on the Ubuntu wiki: https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Artwork/Official?action=AttachFile&do=get&target=UbuntuLogo.png
   - The Ubuntu font, ttf-ubuntu-title

* The kubuntu usplash throbber and source code were used for generating this usplash.

